00:52:31.200 --> 00:52:37.799
wasn't monetized in those days. Are there
any lessons that, in like the discussions

00:52:37.799 --> 00:52:44.119
around software patents for example should
take from that era when there were no patents

00:52:44.119 --> 00:52:48.349
so to speak of? And anything else we could
learn about that?

00:52:48.349 --> 00:52:54.739
&gt;&gt;Kurt: Yeah, yeah. I think one could argue
